title: How To Study The Apocalyptic Gospels of Daniel and Revelation // Joshua Maponga
description: Joshua Maponga III explains how to study and understand the apocalyptic literature of the Bible from Daniel to Revelation. Living in the end-times means we must know the TRUTH about the great controversy which is already settled, how not to panic and be anxious. Prophecy (or revelations of the future) helps us to know the results of the match long before it is played. When we see the things predicted happening, then we will know the Bible is true and God is in charge. We can relax knowing that we are on the winning team.
